{{Top|leg}}
'''LTS''' was slang, used by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], for pilots who survived their first couple of missions after completing training and who were considered "likely to survive" on future missions.

